255
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:20,400
[SPEAKER_04] Ne znam ono.

256
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:23,200
[SPEAKER_04] Ja i dan danas obožavam skakati sa visokih stijena.

257
00:28:23,759 --> 00:28:24,640
